    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>sweet potato</strong> and <strong>meat-free mince</strong> (remove the paper if required!) to the pan and cook for 3-4 min or until the meat-free mince has started to brown and the sweet potatoes are starting to colour</p><p>Add your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> to the pan with 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[375ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [500ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>and cook, covered, for 10 min or until the potatoes are fork-tender</p>",
